### ── OFFER SERVICE (/offer) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Akış: submitOffer → approveOffer (Operator) → Order oluşur

### 1. Teklif gönder — Customer Bauer, Audi A4 (MUC)
# @name submitOffer
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/submitOffer
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000004",
  "offeredPrice": 34500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "desiredPickupDate": "2026-08-01",
  "notes": "Ich biete 34.500 EUR für den Audi A4"
}

### 2. Teklifleri listele — Operator
GET {{baseUrl}}/offer/Offers
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}

### 3. Teklifleri listele — Customer Bauer (sadece kendi teklifleri)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offer/Offers
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Teklifi onayla — Operator
### offerId: 1. adımdan dönen ID'yi buraya yaz
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/approveOffer
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}

### 5. Teklifi reddet — Operator (yeni teklif için)
# Önce submitOffer ile yeni teklif oluştur, sonra reddet
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/rejectOffer
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ",
  "notes": "Preis zu niedrig — Mindestpreis 36.000 EUR"
}

### 6. Reddedilen teklifi yeniden gönder — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/offer/resubmitOffer
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ",
  "offeredPrice": 36000.00,
  "notes": "Ich akzeptiere den Mindestpreis"
}